                <h6>Discover the hair routine made for you</h6>
                <p>Hair loss doesn't look the same for everyone. Choose the concern that feels most familiar to see how
                    Q-Renew can help.</p>
                <hr />
                <strong>Select your concern</strong>
                <ul class="tabs" role="tablist">
                    <li>
                        <button class="active" data-bs-toggle="tab" data-bs-target="#crown-thinning" type="button">Crown
